<article id="post-430" class="blog_post post-430 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-kindle category-5">
			
	
	<div class="date_of_post updated">
		<span class="day_post">14</span>
		<span class="month_post">2月</span>
	</div>
		
	<div class="post-content">	
	<header class="post-header">
								<h2 class="post-title entry-title">
				<a href="http://haugenzhays.com/2016/02/14/how-to-find-an-electronic-book/" title="Permalink to 如何寻找电子书" rel="bookmark">如何寻找电子书</a>
			</h2>
							
		
		
										</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-content">
		<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/kindle_cover_neverending_strory__2013__by_kassiopeyasuse-d9hlb6e.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-441"><img class="size-full wp-image-441 alignnone" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/kindle_cover_neverending_strory__2013__by_kassiopeyasuse-d9hlb6e.jpg" alt="kindle_cover_neverending_strory__2013__by_kassiopeyasuse-d9hlb6e" width="600" height="400" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/kindle_cover_neverending_strory__2013__by_kassiopeyasuse-d9hlb6e.jpg 600w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/kindle_cover_neverending_strory__2013__by_kassiopeyasuse-d9hlb6e-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>常见电子书的种类</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">在说怎么下载之前，先说说常见电子书的种类。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">常见电子书一般有一下三种格式：</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>PDF Mobi Equb</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>PDF</strong>是最为常用的格式，对于图片较多或者漫画之类书籍较好</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">优点：几乎所有的阅读器都支持PDF</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">缺点：体积较大/打开时间长</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Mobi</strong>主要的对象是移动设备，例如Kindle（原生Kindle还支持亚马逊格式azw及Word）。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">优点：体积小</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">缺点：支持设备不多</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Equb</strong>主要支持对象是各手机客户端。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">优点：体积小</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">缺点：支持设备不多</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-442"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-442" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" alt="分割线" width="900" height="38" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg 900w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-300x13.jpg 300w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-768x32.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>寻找电子书的几个网站</strong></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-435" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/readfree.jpg" alt="readfree" width="599" height="399" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/readfree.jpg 599w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/readfree-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>readfree.me</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">推荐指数 ★★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">打开速度 ★★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">书籍数量 ★★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">国人的下载网站，支持各种语言所有热门书籍、支持推送/下载/收藏。最近新开的微信公众号支持微信指令推送，实在是下载电子书的良心网站。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-442"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-442" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" alt="分割线" width="900" height="38" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg 900w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-300x13.jpg 300w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-768x32.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-434" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/forfrigg.jpg" alt="forfrigg" width="600" height="400" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/forfrigg.jpg 600w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/forfrigg-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /><strong>forfrigg.com</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">推荐指数 ★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">打开速度   ★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">书籍数量 ★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">号称或内最优秀的电子书下载平台，但其实有点然并卵，不翻墙的话经常打不开啊。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-442"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-442" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" alt="分割线" width="900" height="38" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg 900w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-300x13.jpg 300w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-768x32.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-433" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/chnxp.jpg" alt="chnxp" width="558" height="372" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/chnxp.jpg 558w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/chnxp-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>浩扬电子书城</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">www.chnxp.com.cn</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">推荐指数  ★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">打开速度 ★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">书籍数量 ★★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">使用的次数不多，网络玄幻小说之类的较多，有一些比较冷门的书。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-442"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-442" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg" alt="分割线" width="900" height="38" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线.jpg 900w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-300x13.jpg 300w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/分割线-768x32.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-432" src="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/baiduyun.jpg" alt="baiduyun" width="600" height="400" srcset="http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/baiduyun.jpg 600w, http://haugenzhays.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/baiduyun-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>网盘搜索</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">http://so.baiduyun.me</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">推荐指数  ★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">打开速度 ★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">书籍数量 ★★★★★</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">有些书实在找不到，还是使用百度网盘搜索吧。支持百度谷歌双搜、支持指定格式，而且或许还可以搜到意想不到的东西哦～</p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
